00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,760
And so that's the idea of clipping levels.

79
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:15,240
You set a threshold below that threshold, don't log anything.

80
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:18,360
Love that threshold, start logging.

